    promotionType: external_exports.string().optional().describe("What is being promoted. Use WEBSITE for traffic/conversion campaigns, APP_ANDROID or APP_IOS for app campaigns. DO NOT set for LEAD_GENERATION (auto-handled) or VIDEO_VIEWS/REACH (not required)."),
    pixelId: external_exports.string().optional().describe("TikTok Pixel ID. REQUIRED for CONVERSIONS campaigns (optimization_goal=CONVERT, promotion_type=WEBSITE). Get this from the TikTok Ads Manager \u2192 Assets \u2192 Events \u2192 Web Events. Not needed for LEAD_GENERATION, REACH, or VIDEO_VIEWS."),
    optimizationEvent: external_exports.string().optional().describe("Conversion event to optimise for. REQUIRED when pixelId is provided. Common values: PURCHASE, COMPLETE_REGISTRATION, SUBMIT_FORM, VIEW_CONTENT, ADD_TO_CART, CHECKOUT. Must match an event your pixel is tracking."),
    bid: external_exports.number().optional().describe("Target bid amount. For OCPM (Lead Gen/Conversions) this is the target cost-per-lead or cost-per-conversion (conversion_bid_price). For CPC/CPV this is cost-per-click or cost-per-view (bid_price). Omit for CPM/REACH \u2014 TikTok optimises reach automatically (lowest cost). Omit to use lowest-cost bidding for any objective."),
